        <section id="about">
            <div class="content-heading">
                <h2>ABOUT</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="content-1">
                    <p>Made with utmost care, and keeping in mind of our valuable users, We bring to you HamroCHAT.
                        Hamro in nepali means "Our". It is to describe unity, and togetherness which we plan on bringing
