                    <p>Initially, We have just introduced a basic chatting module, but we have bigger plans for the
                        future <span class="tuned">Stay tuned!</span></p>
                </div>
                <div class="content-2">
                    <img src="imgs/saly.svg" alt="Saly on computer">
                </div>
            </div>
