            <div class="content-heading">
                <h2>FEATURES</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="box-heading">SECURE</div>
                    <div class="box-image">
                        <img src="imgs/secure.svg" alt="secure">
                    </div>
                    <p>Security is what we all yearn for. Thus, You can login/register with your google account, or our
                        secure login. You can rest assure your data will be safe and sound with us.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="box-heading">CHAT</div>
                    <div class="box-image">
                        <img src="imgs/message.svg" alt="message">
                    </div>
                    <p>We make communication easy and simple. From your part of the world, to any part of the world, It
                        is possible and absolutely for free.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="box-heading">USER FRIENDLY UI</div>
                    <div class="box-image">
                        <img src="imgs/chill.svg" alt="chill">
                    </div>
                    <p>Built with great care and keeping in mind the tiniest details, so you can navgiate through the
                        website hassle
                        free. Take a chill pill, and enjoy!</p>
